<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="waterzone">
      <h1>ðŸ’§ Daily Water Intake Tracker</h1>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/signup">Sign Up</a></li>
        <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
        <li><a href="/intake/add">Add Intake</a></li>
        <li><a href="/intake/list">Intake List</a></li>
        <% if (email) { %>
          <li>
            <form action="/logout" style="display:inline;">
              <button type="submit" class="logout-btn">Logout</button>
            </form>
          </li>
        <% } %>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h1>Welcome to Your Daily Water Intake Tracker</h1>
    <p>
      This web app is designed to help you log and monitor your daily water intake.
      By tracking your hydration habits, you can work toward a healthier, more balanced lifestyle.
      Sign up and start keeping your body refreshed and energized!
    </p>

    <section class="featured">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>
          <h3>Simple Daily Logging</h3>
          <p>Easily add your water intake once per day. Stay consistent and never forget your hydration goals.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>History & Insights</h3>
          <p>View your daily intake history in a paginated list. Edit or delete entries if needed.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Track Progress</h3>
          <p>Calculate the difference in intake between two dates, spot trends, and improve your routines.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about">
      <h2>Why Track Your Water Intake?</h2>
      <p>Proper hydration supports overall health, energy, and focus.
      Use this tracker to build positive habits, celebrate your consistency, and stay accountable.</p>
      <p>Join today and start your journey toward a healthier, more hydrated you!</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
